description: Natalia Kaminska is a hunter working for the http://anidb.net/ch1951 [Mage`s Association]. Her job is to find and execute people as the Association determines, for a bounty. She ends up taking http://anidb.net/ch44389 [Emiya Kiritsugu] in as an apprentice, and he eventually succeeds her in that job.
name: Natalia Kaminska
